text: "Heatseeker" is a 1988 song by Australian hard rock band AC/DC. It was taken from their 11th studio album Blow Up Your Video. It went to number 2 in Norway, number 4 in Sweden, number 5 in Australia and number 12 in the United Kingdom. Category:1988 songs Category:AC/DC songs Category:Hard rock songs
title: Heatseeker (song)
